    • addMeasurement

      public boolean addMeasurement​(com.estg.core.Measurement measurement) throws com.estg.core.exceptions.MeasurementException
      Adds a given Measurements to the Measurements collection of Container.
      Specified by:
      addMeasurement in interface com.estg.core.Container
      Parameters:
      measurement - The given Measurements.
      Returns:
      • True, if the given Measurements was added in Measurements collection.
      • False, if the date of given Measurements is equal with an existing Measurements, but the value of both Measurements is equal.
      Throws:
      com.estg.core.exceptions.MeasurementException -
      1. If the given Measurements is null.
      2. If the value of given Measurements is less than 0.
      3. If the date of given Measurements is before the last existing date of Measurements
      4. If the date of given Measurements is equal with an existing Measurements, but the value of both Measurements is different.
